<br>
you auto stick saracen<br>
you cast warbellow for 100(-93)<br>
you cast battle howl for 129(-119)<br>
you attack with provoke for 425(-81)<br>
infiltrator dual wields you with garrote for 224 + 73<br>
you mez infiltrator<br>
you attack with provoke for 409(-7<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
