<br>
Idenitcal buffs do not give separate classes the same benefits. Buffing an infiltrator/sb/ns with dex/quick will benefit his evade chance 7 times as much as it will benefit your evade chance with exactly the same dex/quick bonuses. <br>
<br>
This creates a problem where certain classes which would otherwise be somewhat balanced w/o buffs are now completely and utterly unbalanced giving the same level of buffs to both characters.<br>
<br>
Not saying assassin vs skald is a fair fight w/o buffs but it sure is 10x harder vs a buffed assassin even if you have max buffs as well.<br>
<br>
